    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a peerless 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with the critical subframe reinforcement already completed and a recent rod bearing service for preventative maintenance. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. The chassis remains taut, riding on OEM-spec Bilstein dampers with zero bushing deflection. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic with a showroom-quality interior, this vehicle maintains its original factory tolerances and includes a comprehensive service dossier. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
