    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory finish, completely free from stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Every body panel aligns perfectly, reflecting its accident-free history. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of pristine leather and untouched trim; it still carries that distinct new-car aroma, with absolutely no wear on the seat bolsters, steering wheel, or switchgear. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with every service performed on time and fully documented. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of salt or corrosion. Every electronic feature, from the premium sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as intended. This is a collector-grade example for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. Includes all original keys, factory manuals, and a custom-fit car cover.",
